                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3c82513w/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>numerous articles that have been inserted therein complimentary<lb/> to <persName>Mr\n                    Isaacs</persName> whom they despise—and this last<lb/> article is not likely to\n                diminish the prejudice—</p>\n            <p>I regret exceedingly that you did not publish<lb/> the communications relative to the\n                Ladies singing<lb/> but nevertheless I sincerely believe you<lb/> suppressed them\n                with the purest motives</p>\n            <p>I have not as yet informed the Ball Committee<lb/> of the Donation &amp; Tickets but\n                I will attend to<lb/> it either to day or to morrow</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I am my dear sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">your faithful Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Ansel Leo</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>To <addressee>Revd I. Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">&amp;c &amp;c</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3c82513w/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
